Products.FullDescription: Abbott's Village Bakery Light Rye Bread
Products.RichDescription:
EVERY BIT BETTERAbbott’s Village Bakery® believes in making the most of every mouthful. We bake every loaf to be so full of flavour, texture and aroma that it’s absolutely irresistible. Work your topping magic, and savour every last crumb.?

This dark (not-so) mysterious loaf has us all running for its deep and malty flavours. Our softer twist on the classic is baked with our home-grown rye flour and topped with a sprinkle of semolina to give a gentle crunch. It’s perfect for a Reuben sandwich… or really any way you like it.

Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Abbott's Village Bakery Country Grains' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription:
Abbott’s Village Bakery® Country Grains. A loaf that you'll be savouring down to the very last crumb.

Every bit better (compared to Abbott's Village Bakery product in the market in January 2018).

Abbott’s Village Bakery® believes in making the most of every mouthful. We bake every loaf to be so full of flavour, texture and aroma that it’s absolutely, positively irresistible. Now it’s over to you. Work your topping magic, and savour every last crumb.

Country grains makes the perfect base for caramelised banana and peanut butter toast.

This loaf definitely goes with the grain. A colourful combo of mixed kibbled grains including purple wheat, red sorghum, rye, wheat, triticale, corn, barley, and kibbled soy gives serious crunch. To ensure you get maximum flavour out of this loaf, we’ve finished it off with a sprinkling of toasted oats over the top.

Suitable for vegetarians and vegans.

No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.

Products.RichDescription:
Abbott’s Village Bakery Rustic White has no artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.

Abbott's Village Bakery believes in making the most of every mouthful. We bake every loaf to be so full of flavour, texture and aroma that it's absolutely, positively irresistible. Now it's over to you. Work your topping magic, and savour every last crumb.

You can't go wrong with a classic. Especially when it's this soft. And this loaf tastes as good as it feels, thanks to a dash of rye flour that gives a subtle earthy flavour. Oh yes, and a dusting of semolina adds a lovely crusty finish.
